title: Ace Drummond Old Time Serial (OTS) (1936)
description:
This is one of many serials which were run at movie theaters, one per week, normally on Saturdays to keep kids coming back every Saturday until the end of the serial.  This was in the 30s, 40s and 50s.  They finally died out as the price became too high to justify this "freeby" being offered by theater owners.

I have a bunch of these.  If they prove to be popular (many seeds), I will continue to upload so don't just download and delete, SEED THESE YOURSELF to speed propagation and lower my data rate.
